      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey SciValidator, we're implementing some updates to the submission workflow starting next month. We're moving away from the purely algorithmic screening and transitioning to a \"Global Equity\" model to ensure we aren't overlooking important research from non-traditional institutions. Just wanted to run this by you before we start the migration plan.",
